1. Downloaded and installed Node.js
2. Verified installation using "node -v" and "npm -v"
3. Navigated into the alx-intermediate-frontend repository
4. Created the directory "0x03-sass_scss"
5. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using the command: npm install sass@3.7.4
6. Verified the installation with: npx sass --version
7. Tested by compiling a .scss file into .css
